sequenceDiagram
    participant User as CSM (User)
    participant UI as Frontend (React/WebSockets)
    participant API as Backend (FastAPI)
    participant DB as Postgres (Supabase)
    participant ML as ML Pipeline
    participant Bot as Voice/Email Agents

    User->>UI: 1. Sign in to Dashboard
    User->>UI: 2. Upload Database / Excel Data
    UI->>API: Send raw customer data
    API->>DB: Store standardized records
    
    User->>UI: 3. Customize Formulas & Settings
    UI->>API: Save configuration
    
    API->>ML: 4. Trigger ML Pipeline
    ML->>DB: Fetch Account Data
    ML-->>ML: Calculate Health, Churn & Upsell
    ML->>DB: Update Opportunities & Scores
    
    DB-->>API: Data updated
    API-->>UI: Dashboard stats updated
    
    API->>Bot: 5. Trigger Automated Campaigns
    Bot->>Bot: Engage customer (Voice/Email)
    Bot->>API: 6. Webhooks (Call Status/Transcripts)
    
    API->>DB: Save interaction logs & sentiment
    API-->>UI: 7. Real-time WebSocket Alert (Call Finished/Risk Detected)
    UI-->>User: Display Live Alerts & Updated Dashboard
